PWA: installable app, offline service worker, web-push notifications

- Icons: generate branded PWA/favicon/apple-touch icons (were missing).
- Manifest: standalone app, proper any+maskable icons, theme.
- Service worker: offline app-shell (SPA-aware caching) + push + notificationclick handlers.
- Install prompt + notification toggle in the footer (PwaControls).
- Web push backend: web-push dep, PushSubscription model, /api/push routes
  (vapid-public-key, subscribe, unsubscribe), and a util that notifies a case
  owner when their case gets a verdict (degrades gracefully if VAPID unset).
- Mobile: viewport-fit=cover for safe areas.

Requires VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY / VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY / VAPID_SUBJECT env vars
(documented in backend/.env.example); set them in Railway to enable push.

